SUMMARY TABLE
================================================================================
Suffix  | Keys                                              | Notes
--------|---------------------------------------------------|----------------------
A       | t, RF2, U2                                        | nested part->node->time
A2      | t, RF2, U2                                        | flat part->time
B       | t, S11, S12, S22                                  | elem->time->int_pts
C       | t, COOR1, COOR2                                   | node->time coords
C2      | t, nodes_time, elements, adjacency,               | hex mesh topology
        |   baricenters, normals                            |
D       | t, stresses                                       | elem->(S11,S22) per t
T1      | t, nodes, elements, elements_area,                | triangulation interp
        |   elements_area_normalized                        | has MESH_ID in name
T2      | t, time_variant, time_invariant,                  | triangulation stats +
        |   general_information, eta,                       | geometry/kinematics
        |   edge_sizes, q, epsilon, F,                      | has MESH_ID in name
        |   shear, gle,                                     |
        |   shear_mean, gle_mean,                           |
        |   edi, edi_mean                                   |
H1/J1/  | t, nodes, bars, bars_connectivity                 | bar geometry+stress
I1      |                                                   |
K1      | t, nodes, nodes_id, nodes_stress, bars,           | bar + Abaqus IDs
        |   bars_connectivity, bars_meth2                   |
H2/I2/  | t, tension, compression                           | NetworkX graphs/t
J2/K2   |                                                   |
H3/I3/  | t, global_ef_t, global_ef_c                       | scalar efficiency/t
J3/K3   |                                                   |
